   Grand Hôtel du Lac Vevey

Location

Private transfer

    The hotel is located 1.5km from Vevey town centre and railway station
    (less than 10 mins on foot) and 90km from Geneva airport (60 mins by
                               train or car).

   A secured car parking of 16 places with valet parking is available upon
                      reservation and at an extra cost.

                    Certified TESLA Destination Charging

   To insure your entire comfort, our Concierges offer their services to
   organise your arrival with elegance in our luxurious Mercedes-Benzes
   limousines.

   Our Mercedes-Benz S Class Limousine accommodates comfortably 3 people.
   Our Mercedes-Benz Viano accommodates comfortably 7 people (adults or
   children).
     * Geneva international airport (60 min drive)
     * TGV Lausanne railway station (30 min drive)
     * Vevey railway station / town center (5 min walk)


   For groups of more than 8 people, vehicles with higher capacity can be
   provided.

Useful details

Arrival & departure

   Rooms are available from 3:00pm onwards, checkout is until noon. While
   every effort will be made to provide you with a room upon your arrival,
   access to rooms can only be guaranteed before 3:00pm if you make a
   reservation for an additional night before your stay. Late departure is
   subject to availability and may incur additional charges. Cancellations
   and no-shows incur payment for the entire duration of the stay.
   Cancellation conditions may vary, depending on the period of your trip
   and the fare plan chosen at the time of booking.

   Private and secure paid parking Private and secure paid parking

   Pets welcomed at an additional charge Pets welcomed at an additional
   charge

   Accessible for people with reduced mobility Accessible for people with
   reduced mobility

   Meeting rooms available for 2 to 300 people Meeting rooms available for
   2 to 300 people

   TESLA Destination Charging TESLA Destination Charging

